<img width="500" height="305" class="wp-image-1551034" style="width: 600px;" src="https://cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/AISHA-e1650750610341.gif" alt="Aisha Buhari"> Political gladiators and big wigs have started coming to the venue of the All Progressives Congress, APC’s convention. The wife of the president, Aisha Buhari is currently at the Eagle Square. The senate president, Ahmed Lawan is equally present. Lawan was cheered by many believed to be his supporters when he came in.  Governor of Ekiti state John Olukayode Fayemi, is equally at the venue.  As at the time of filling this report, many dignitaries are currently seated waiting for the commencement of the convention.